I’m more of a PC person rather than a Mac, but if I remember correctly. “0x1018e8146” is in scientific notation and means this in human standards: 1018 x 10[sup]8146[/sup]. I am most likely sure that is what it is. Have you installed any hardware recently or any software at all? It could be a problem with that. The memory could be the RAM.
